    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. Essential preventative maintenance is addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The chassis benefits from a suspension refresh, utilizing polyurethane bushings for enhanced lateral stiffness and steering response. While the exterior and cabin show signs of regular use, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, delivering the quintessential analog driving experience expected from this generation of M-car.",
