      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of luxury and dependability. The exterior maintains a brilliant luster with only minor, age-appropriate character marks, while the interior is exceptionally clean, smoke-free, and features leather upholstery that remains supple and supportive. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and has been serviced religiously at 5,000-mile intervals; the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless. It provides a quiet, composed ride that feels solid on the highway and nimble in the city. This is a well-loved car that is ready for its next chapter with a driver who appreciates a vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
